{File:FXI_IS.txt  Index:10  Index Date:20170524  PL:66.67%  PS:33.33%  Trades:6  CL:1}

IF HIGH OF 2 BARS AGO > HIGH OF 1 BARS AGO
AND HIGH OF 1 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO > HIGH OF 3 BARS AGO
AND HIGH OF 3 BARS AGO > HIGH OF 5 BARS AGO
AND HIGH OF 5 BARS AGO > HIGH OF 4 BARS AGO
THEN BUY NEXT BAR ON THE OPEN WITH
PROFIT TARGET AT ENTRY PRICE + 1.6964106 %
AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 1.6020506 %
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
